title: Mendelssohn - Overtures - Flor, Bamberg SO
description:
Mendelssohn: Overtures.

A collection of favourite overtures by Felix Mendelssohn, recorded by Claus Peter Flor and the Bamberg Symphony Orchestra and released by RCA Victor in 1988.

Note: The Penguin Guide editors not only gave this recording a rosette, but had this to say: "This is the most desirable collection of Mendelssohn overtures the catalogue has ever offered."

I strongly suggest you acquire this recording, my classical loving friends; you will enjoy it!

MP3 @ 320
